question: Ūi-hô "Parametric (PM)" chit khoán lūi-hêng ê model ū kúi-ê?
Kui-á ê model category siâu ū siok chē model tī piáu lāi?
Chiu chhut só͘-ū model ê miâ, in-ū in ê 'Note' ū chū-bêng sī kiat-lâi chū 'return of yields'.
Ūi-hô 'Historical simulation (HS)' kāi-á lāi-té, kám-chhiáⁿ hō͘-miâ ē-tàng kóng-ê kî-tiong ê tē-it êModel（FHS），i kám-chhiáⁿ ū kau-lāi chìn-hêng liáⁿ ê tiau-siāu?
Tī liàn-phài ê tsuân-pōo bô-hîng tang-tiong, ū to-tsē phah-suànn ê sī hō-tsò 'Neural network (NN)'?
Thè-tâi lāi-bīn, ū hiah-ê model category sī siōng bē su-iàu ê, hō͘ i chin bē hū kó͘-seng?
Nāi-koán ūi suài hē thîng-chú ēng teh hō-chò "return of yields" ê só͘-ū model, chiūⁿ tō hō͘ in chò chi̍t ê sin ê "Returns-Based" classifier, chi̍t ê sin ê classifier liáu-āu chiū ē ū kúi-ê model?
Za "Model Name" li, "Parametric" category to, a-siaⁿ-ê siⁿ-hoat chòe "return of yields" kap chòe "yields" ê khòaⁿ-māi ê kiōng-tông ê bōe-á (suffix) sī siáⁿ-mih?
answer: Koh-iā ê bōe-á sī '_RET'. Che ē-tàng khòaⁿ-māi-ê sī pí-kàu 'AR' (model of yields) kap 'AR_RET' (model of return of yields) í-ki̍p 'GARCH' kap 'GARCH_RET'.

question: Kā 'CGAN-FC' kap 'CGAN-LSTM' ê su-kì lâi kóng, tī 'Neural network (NN)' ê khu-hūn lāi-bīn, ē-tàng ìn-tōaⁿ ē-tàng chaiáⁿ-iūⁿ ê koan-hē chāi-chāiModel ê miâ-lē kap i ê ki-chho· kiàn-chio̍h ê tiong-kan?
answer: Ē-tàng ìn-tōaⁿ chi̍t ê ti̍t-chiap ê koan-hē, chiàⁿ-sek tī 'Model Name' ê āu-chhui (chhiūⁿ-chhiūⁿ '-FC', '-LSTM') sī kā 'Note' lāi-bīn ê liáu-kài kóng ê bôa-chāi-chāi bôa-chāi bôa-chāi bôa-chāi bôa-chāi bôa-chāi hō-sî bôa-chāi bôa-chāi bôa-chāi bôa-chāi bôa-chāi bôa-chāi bôa-chāi liáu-kài Model ê kiàn-chio̍h, che sī piáu-bī chi̍t ê chiàⁿ-sek ê miâ-chheng-hoat lâi tú bôa-chāi chi̍t ê Model ê kiàn-chio̍h.

question: Koh phiah "Parametric (PM)" kap "Neural network (NN)" chit nn̄g ê mn̄g, in-lāi êMODEL ê sò͘-liōng ū cheng-chha bô? Nā-sī tùi in ê biâu-siâu lâi khòaⁿ, gip-búi êMODEL-lāi ê hong-huat khah chē ê sīlāi chi̍t ê mn̄g?
answer: "Neural network (NN)" mn̄g êMODEL khah ū chē ê bô-kāng-khoán ê hong-huat. "Parametric (PM)" êMODEL chú-iàu sī ki-chāi AR kap GARCH téng-téng kó͘-tiāu ê ki-su̍t lâi chè-chō, chú-iàu sī khòaⁿ iōng-tâi ia̍h-sī iâⁿ-lī ê chu-liāu ia̍h-sī bô-chiàⁿ chē ê kui-chek; tān-sī "Neural network (NN)" mn̄g êMODEL sī ū chin chē bô-kāng-khoán ê ki-su̍t, chhin-chhiūⁿ CGAN, CWGAN, Diffusion model, kap VAE téng-téng, in-lāi êMODEL-lāi ê hong-huat khah chē ê sīlāi chi̍t ê mn̄g.

question: PHS 係指啥物？伊是按怎款的 Model？
answer: PHS 係指 Plain Historical Simulation，伊是 Historical simulation (HS) Model。
